The paper focuses on improving the performance of convolution in deep neural networks, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method also aims to reduce memory consumption, which is a concern in many areas of computer science, including neural networks (cs.NE), data structures (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
